latestIgtvVideos.title: More than just a poem for India.
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Going through a lot and seeing so happening much around, Crying myself to sleep and wondering who’s next and what might just happen tomorrow. I’m scared now and we don’t have single person to blame on because there are plenty other. Whole country is affected and people have lost there everything what’s even worse than this.
Thanks to doctors, police and everyone working to make things little comfortable for us and giving a ray of hope♥️
This poem is dedicated to India 🇮🇳 I do love you India but this time you failed.
If you like this do share ♥️🙏🏻
.
.
.
.
.

latestIgtvVideos.title: STOP PUTTING PRESSURE ON US IN LOCKDOWN
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Had to write this poem And I know with me I know most of you would be feeling same combing back home leaving our career aside wasn’t easy it’s wasn’t our choice but today after one year when everyone is asking what next, I really don’t have any answer, we all don’t have and that’s Ohkay. It’s the most confusing phase of life well it’s life at least. Parents pressure is not helpful at this point, please do understand it’s not only your kids facing and figuring out things it’s most of us right now, they are not doing anything because the whole world is taken away from them, trust them if they really wanna do something they would at any cost other wise maybe try to give them space and time. 
And if youuu to feel the same don’t give up please life is big and phases are small keep going because you still need to shine✨
Share this with people who want this to listen, show your parents ♥️
I hope you too could relate with the poem ♥️
.
.
.
.
